OL,3,CCommunity draws up plans to fight
OL,4,Chundreds of broadband poles
OL,6,FResidents are drawing up plans to
OL,7,Ffight the installation of hundreds of
OL,8,Fbroadband poles in an East Yorkshire
OL,9,Ftown.
OL,11,FA packed public meeting in Beverly
OL,12,Fheard from objectors who say the
OL,13,Finfrastructure, which is not subject
OL,14,Fto standard planning rules, will make
OL,15,Ftheir streets look like the 1950s.
OL,17,FResidents from nearby Hedon, Hull, who
OL,18,Fare campaigning against a similar
OL,19,Fscheme, have offered their help.
