OL,3,CCommunity draws up plans to fight
OL,4,Chundreds of broadband poles
OL,6,FCllr Steve Gallant from East Riding of
OL,7,FYorkshire Council said: "A number of
OL,8,Fcampaigners in Hedon, where we have
OL,9,Fbeen fighting this for the past four
OL,10,Fmonths, have been coming along to
OL,11,Fshare experiences about what works and
OL,12,Fwhat doesn't work and what people can
OL,13,Fdo to slow the process down.
OL,15,F"We are that hoping out of this
OL,16,Fmeeting that the locals will get
OL,17,Fthemselves organised into a campaign
OL,18,Fgroup like we did."
