OL,3,CCommunity draws up plans to fight
OL,4,Chundreds of broadband poles
OL,6,FThe campaign group in held several
OL,7,Fhigh-profile public meetings and
OL,8,Fprotests over the issue, insisting
OL,9,Fthat infrastructure should be
OL,10,Funderground - a view shared by people
OL,11,Fin Beverley.
OL,13,FOne protester at the meeting said the
OL,14,Fpoles were a "blot on the landscape".
OL,16,FAnother resident described them as
OL,17,F"ugly" and complained they were being
OL,18,Ferected alongside "nice" lamp stands
OL,19,Fwith "wires being strung all over the
OL,20,Fplace."
