OL,3,CCommunity draws up plans to fight
OL,4,Chundreds of broadband poles
OL,6,FCllr Sue Steel, from East Riding of
OL,7,FYorkshire Council, criticised the
OL,8,Finstallation scheme saying the
OL,9,Ftelecommunications companies are
OL,10,F"ruining our historic towns and
OL,11,Fvillages".
OL,13,FConnexin, the company due to install
OL,14,Fthe poles, said in a statement: "We
OL,15,Fare a local business and are bringing
OL,16,Fcompetition and choice to our region.
OL,17,FWhere possible, our build approach
OL,18,Falways puts the use of any exisiting
OL,19,Finfrastructure first."
